name: src/NOV_ACTIONS.js
openNotePad
description: NOV_ACTIONS - opens the application

params.name: verify
params.description: verifies that the app is open and visible

params.name: restart
params.description: Restarts the app before attempting to open

name: closeNotePad
description: NOV_ACTIONS - closes the application

params.name: verify
params.description: verifies that the app is open and visible

params.name: click
params.description: uses clicks to close notepad if true, otherwises uses keyboard shortcuts

params.name: bypassSaveDialog
params.description: if true clicks don't save if the save dialog exists

name: navOption
description: NOV_ACTIONS - Represents a navigation option for our application

params.name: root
params.description: the root menu, File, Edit, etc...

params.name: option
params.description: the secondary option

params.name: keys
params.description: optional keyboard shortcut if the menu item supports it

name: root
description: the root menu, File, Edit, etc...

name: option
description: the secondary option

name: keys
description: optional keyboard shortcut if the menu item supports it

name: path
description: the full combined path of. root|path

name: action
description: Performs actions on the nav option

params.name: click
params.description: uses clicks to otherwises uses keyboard shortcuts

name: navOptions
description: NOV_ACTIONS - holds nav options created by {@link navOption}

properties.name: exit
properties.description: nav option for exiting / closing notepad

properties.name: save
properties.description: nav option for saving a file

name: menuNavigation
description: NOV_ACTIONS - performs various menu navigation options

params.name: option
params.description: which option to perform from {@link navOptions}

params.name: click
params.description: uses clicks to otherwises uses keyboard shortcuts

name: inputTestData
description: NOV_ACTIONS - inputs data from a test data object

params.name: data
params.description: the data to input / verify

params.name: clear
params.description: if true clears the text first

params.name: newLine
params.description: if true automatically enters a new line after each test data input

params.name: verify
params.description: if true verifies the app accepts input properly

return.description: data - returns our test data with the expectedData property set (so we can keep passing this around)

name: saveDialog
description: NOV_ACTIONS - performs actions and verfies the save dialog existence

params.name: selectOption
params.description: which option to select, save, don'tsave or cancel

params.name: click
params.description: uses clicks to otherwises uses keyboard shortcuts. only click is supported currently

params.name: verifyExists
params.description: verfies the dialog actually exists

name: saveToFile
description: NOV_ACTIONS - saves the data we have inputed into a file

params.name: nav
params.description: if true handles the menu navigation for saving

params.name: newFile
params.description: if assumes we aren't editing and resaving so we will have the dialog to save too

params.name: data
params.description: test data to save

params.name: click
params.description: uses clicks to otherwises uses keyboard shortcuts. only click is supported currently

params.name: verify
params.description: verfies the file is created after saving

return.description: data - returns our test data with the savedFile property set (so we can keep passing this around)

params.name: message

params.name: fileName

name: getTestData
description: NOV_DATA - Obtains test data of a specific type

params.name: type
params.description: {@link testDataTypes}
